      <em><h3>How do I add a new result?</h3></em>
      <p>To add a new result please ensure you have registered then, log in to your profile and click dashboard. At the top of the page you will see a green box with various drop down options, select the game you are playing, your opponent and enter the score. Once you click add you will be directed to the <em>"my-games"</em> page where you will see all the latest results.</p>
