    <div class="question">
      <em><h3>How to view the leagues page?</h3></em>
      <p>This is accessed through the navigation at the top of every page whether logged-in or not. If javascript is disabled on your browser then this will take you to a <em><a href="/leagues">page with links to the various leagues</a></em> </p>
    </div>

    <div class="question">
      <em><h3>What happens if I add the wrong result?</h3></em>
      <p>If the wrong result is added then please log-in using then link above and go to <em><a href="/dashboard/my-games">your games</a></em> or find the link for this on the left side of your dashboard and scroll down to the correct game and click edit, you will then be taken to another page where you can edit the selected game.</p>
    </div>

